column3:
<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
The bladewise Hoobigo is eyeing you with interest.
Survey the designated location and defeat any challengers that appear.
You're part of the Third Promise's retinue, aren't you? Not many could stand a chance against Gulool Ja Ja in combat, shade or not. Been eager for a chance to take the measure of you.
The young warriors who once trained here have long since left the forest in search of work. But Whetstone still has plenty of fighting spirit.
Sure, we're all getting on in years, but we fought hand-to-hand with the Xbr'aal during the war. Our scales are stronger than steel.
Care to test your mettle against Mamook's finest? I'll gather my comrades and meet you north of here. When you're ready, come and find us─and once victory's been decided, we'll meet back here.
A victory worthy of your accolades, stranger. I only hope my hip makes a full recovery...
Whetstone was once a gathering of young blood eager to sharpen their scales. Ah, to be young again...
You've done an admirable job on your own scales, if I do say so myself. Does an old warrior proud.
I suppose our time on the field is well and truly done. Now, we must do what we can to pass on our knowledge to those who would learn it.
You have my thanks. My comrades and I will learn from our battle, and see that Whetstone hones the scales of many a young warrior to come.
